Program: Discovery
Title: Climate Wars - part two
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrymc
Last Broadcast Date: 24 February 2004
The UN framework convention on climate change, and the consensus needed to enforce it. The programme examines the convention which emerged from the Rio World Summit of 1992 and the Kyoto Protocol of 1997. The Unites States has rejected the protocol and now relies on Russia to sign it.